    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The thruneosaurus's eyes project a line of fire in a @Template[type:line|distance:30], dealing @Damage[(floor(@actor.level/2))d6[fire]] damage for every 2 levels the thruneosaurus has to all creatures in the area (@Check[type:reflex|against:hellfire-gaze|basic:true]). A creature that critically fails its save also takes persistent fire damage equal to the number of damage dice. This uses a trained DC using the thruneosaurus's Constitution modifier or an expert DC if the beast is specialized.</p>",
